                        p 収納便利
        .block-info
            .container
                .title ニュース
                .info-card
                    .info-card-item
                        a(href='https://www.zeczec.com/projects/wirecare?r=6a7b61f2d9' target='blank')
                            img(src='../../styles/images/wirecare-info/reuseImages/info1-jp.jpg' alt='')
                            .card-title.faq
                                | 支援者数2166人!
